The control catalogue in internal/framework/ecc_catalog.json is derived from
the Essential Cybersecurity Controls (ECC-2:2024) published by the National
Cybersecurity Authority of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. That document is
published by the NCA and remains its work; it is reproduced here as reference
data for assessment purposes.

    https://nca.gov.sa/en/regulatory-documents/controls-list/ecc/

The catalogue is parsed from the published PDF by internal/framework/parse_ecc.py.
Entries marked "needs_review" could not be cleanly extracted and must be
verified against the official document before being relied upon.
